 StyleBox["SpinDynamica",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " may be used to construct three-dimensional right-angled axis systems. "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.640885139204935*^9, 
  3.640885179435854*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"6282e522-d419-4e78-9530-\
b1d23c729eb2"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "By default ",
 StyleBox["AxisSystem[]",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " returns a set of unit vectors along the x, y and z-axes:"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.640885186220338*^9, 
  3.640885215473867*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"2e9cd672-4eb4-4790-a0f0-\
