Cell["\<\
The orientation of the x and y axes returned by AxisSystem may be controlled \
by providing another vector to the routine. The x-axis of the returned axis \
system is defined to be in the plane of the two input vectors. In the case \
below, the x-axis of the returned axis system is the zy-plane of the \
reference frame.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.640885322671384*^9, 3.6408853723345222`*^9}, {
  3.6414894997639837`*^9, 3.6414895020322537`*^9}, {3.641699358519023*^9, 
