   SubscriptBox["CO", "2"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "42ee024b-9742-4caf-bc84-3f79c69e03ef"],
 " plane, and y-axis perpendicular to the plane, may be constructed as \
follows:"
}], "Text",
